				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/09/28/4598-ils-ont-decide-de-laisser-les-autres-travailler-pour-eux?replytocom=19031#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-19031", "19031", "respond", "4598")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
